file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - LIST OF SERVICE BULLETINS

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL SERVICE BULLETIN LIST This list is intended to guide the operator as to which Service Bulletins are incorporated to the MPP (Maintenance Practices and Procedures). The list consists of: the Service Bulletin Number and its revision (if applicable) and the affected task(s) (MPP Task Number), information on whether the Service Bulletin affects the manual. A revision bar will be placed on the left margin of the list whenever data are inserted or revised.
